# 🎮 Hangman Game

A simple Python-based Hangman Game where players guess a hidden word one letter at a time before running out of chances.

## 📌 Features

- Random word selection
- Letter-by-letter guessing
- Tracks remaining chances
- Win and lose conditions
- Beginner-friendly Python project

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Random Module

🎯 Gameplay
The game randomly selects a word.
You have 6 chances to guess the word.
Enter one letter at a time.
Correct guesses reveal letters.
Incorrect guesses reduce remaining chances.
Guess the word before your chances run out.

📚 Learning Outcomes
Working with lists
Loops and conditions
User input handling
Random module usage
Basic game development logic

